                "invention-title": [
                    "Solar hydrogen-rich electricity-storage heat-storage vacuum cup",
                    "一种太阳能富氢储电储热保温杯"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of solar technology application, in particular to a solar hydrogen-rich electricity and heat storage vacuum cup which comprises a cup body, the cup body comprises an outer wall, a middle wall and an inner wall, a vacuum heat insulation cavity is formed between the outer wall and the middle wall, a flexible photovoltaic panel is arranged in the vacuum heat insulation cavity, and a phase change heat storage cavity is formed between the middle wall and the inner wall; a phase change heat storage material is arranged in the phase change heat storage cavity, and a water storage cavity is formed in the inner wall; the cup base is arranged at the bottom of the cup body, an electricity storage assembly and a hydrogen production assembly are arranged in the cup base, and the electricity storage assembly is connected with the flexible photovoltaic panel and the hydrogen production assembly; and the cup cover is arranged at the top of the cup body. Drinking water is changed into hydrogen-rich water through electrolytic hydrogen production, so that the body health is benefited; the flexible photovoltaic panel generates electricity to provide electrolysis electricity, the electricity is stored in the electricity storage assembly, and the electricity storage assembly can serve as an emergency power supply to be suitable for charging other equipment, so that the dependence on the environment is reduced, the environmental pollution is reduced, and the actual effects of energy conservation and efficiency improvement are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及太阳能技术应用技术领域，具体涉及一种太阳能富氢储电储热保温杯，包括：杯体，杯体包括外壁和中壁、以及内壁，外壁与中壁之间形成真空隔热腔，柔性光伏板设于真空隔热腔内，中壁与内壁之间形成相变储热腔，相变储热腔内设有相变储热材料，内壁内设有储水腔；杯座，设于杯体的底部，杯座内设有储电组件和制氢组件，储电组件与柔性光伏板和制氢组件连接；杯盖，设于杯体的顶部。电解制氢使饮用水变为富氢水，有益于身体健康；通过柔性光伏板发电提供电解用电，同时储存于储电组件内，该储电组件可以作为应急电源适用为其他设备充电适用，减少了对所处环境的依赖，并减轻了环境污染，达到了节能增效的实际效用。"
                }
            ]
